I have to take my
director's punishment,

00:52:09.770 --> 00:52:12.440
because she's asked me to keep
my mouth shut till my show.

00:52:12.440 --> 00:52:13.080
Save you voice.

00:52:13.080 --> 00:52:14.390
LILLETE DUBEY: Not that she's
doing anything of the kind.

00:52:14.390 --> 00:52:16.098
RAJESHWARI SACHDEV:
